AddressInfo.Title: St Martin's Gate Car Park
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Rapid chargepoint is situated next to a parent and child bay in a pay and display car park, when you enter the car park follow the lane up to the end, then turn right and go down the adjacent lane as directed. Turn left at the end of this lane and the rapid chargepoint is immediately on your left. Access hours: 7.00 to 21.00. Parking fees apply. Max stay in the charging bay 1 hour.

GeneralComments: Pay by Charge Your Car RFID card, or by using the APP (available through Google Play or Apple), or by phoning the number on the chargepoint and paying by credit or debit card. Chargepoint is also available on the Polar Plus network for Polar Plus members (electricity cost of £0.108/kWh).
